metadata.name: fatigue salad
metadata.description: Progressive is super slow NFT art. It imitates JPEG image loading under a slow network to make you think about how to deal with art. It takes 24 hours from the last mint to complete the art. You can also mint a snapshot in progress. But if someone mints it, the same art will never appear again.
